channel.title: MoparCalc
channel.description:
This is a really basic calculator that I made. I started it a few days ago but stopped because I got bored with it. I decided to finish it today when moparisthebest thought I didn't know Java or something.... I made this really fast, and i was trying to show that I know how to do different things. I do know that there are better ways i could have done things but I really don't care atm.
PS: moparisthebest I also made an IRC bot a few weeks ago. PM me if you want to see it.
